Global minerals processing, material and cement giant FLSmidth will be using Electra Mining Africa both to excite customers with the power of digitisation in its new technology and inspire a stronger partnership with mines by taking more responsibility for process efficiency in plants. This article first appeared in Mining Review Africa Issue 8 2018. It will be published online on the 14th September 2018. You can read the full digital magazine here or subscribe here to receive a print copy